{"tid":1832138,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"丹麥美人魚像遭噴FREE HONG KONG","createTime":"2020-01-21T03:01:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-21T11:50:38.000Z","uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"cf943d5133bbf0f54d241c028b965c53c81091ba","tid":1832138,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:01:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200114/s00002/1578939428710/%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5%E7%BE%8E%E4%BA%BA%E9%AD%9A%E5%83%8F%E9%81%AD%E5%99%B4free-hong-kong\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200114%2Fs00002%2F1578939428710%2F%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%2583%258F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2599%25B4free-hong-kong&d=DnofPF37Lcb9g14kkk4r6hdyOQTk4RMct2Rsqyof94c%3D&h=70b5fb7b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200114%2Fs00002%2F1578939428710%2F%25E4%25B8%25B9%25E9%25BA%25A5%25E7%25BE%258E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%25AD%259A%25E5%2583%258F%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2599%25B4free-hong-kong&h=61ce561b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200114/s00002/1578939428710/%E4%B8%B9%E9%BA%A5%E7%BE%8E%E4%BA%BA%E9%AD%9A%E5%83%8F%E9%81%AD%E5%99%B4free-hong-kong</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】丹麥著名景點「小美人魚雕像（The Little Mermaid）」，被人以紅色油漆於雕像下的大石寫上「FREE HONG KONG」字句，當地警方正搜尋線索。旅遊界立法會議員姚思榮認為尚無證據顯示何人所為，但此舉「無品」，應「引以為鑑」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據丹麥《本地報》（The Local Denmark）報道，位於哥本哈根朗格利尼海濱（ Langelinie promenade）的小美人魚雕像，當地時間星期日晚上或周一早上被人破壞，以紅色油漆於雕像下的大石寫上「FREE HONG KONG」，旁邊亦有白色油漆寫上同樣字句。《本地報》引述當地報章稱，當地警方正盡力搜尋線索，並派出警犬搜索任何有關物品。<br />\n<br />\n姚思榮認為現時尚無證據顯示何人所為，港人予人印象「守法、理性」，加上外遊經驗多，於公眾場所多注重禮儀，近年已甚少聽聞港人外遊「失禮」。他續說，香港和海外均有充足渠道表達政治訴求，塗鴉具歷史價值的雕像十分「無品」，也影響國際對港人印象，涉事者從自己角度出發，沒考慮受眾感受，既「達不到目的」，更是以身試法，「希望是最後一次」，港人亦須「引以為鑑」。<br />\n<br />\n丹麥小美人魚雕像有107年歷史，1913年由丹麥雕塑家愛德華艾瑞克森（Edvard Eriksen）根據安徒生童話和妻子愛琳艾瑞克森（Eline Eriksen）為藍本雕塑，雕像以往曾屢次遭人塗鴉。<br />\n<br />\n（反修例風暴）"},{"pid":"845284a09a330a560a45578be082d01085fff06f","tid":1832138,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:03:58.000Z","msg":"衰咩?"},{"pid":"0bdcc0e4505dc98d8b19a886053240a36980bd3e","tid":1832138,"uid":345490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:05:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"722a141bea7e405af755f4a69699c4f4dcc1c810","tid":1832138,"uid":144541,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:08:15.000Z","msg":"Old news"},{"pid":"f5830104aacf44e7f21a2305d63daa263b5fa393","tid":1832138,"uid":61974,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:11:39.000Z","msg":"當地手足清潔返啦，仲po old news"},{"pid":"4815774d94be628db41af6e11d1111ba0ad80952","tid":1832138,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T03:41:23.000Z","msg":"崇尚自由嘅北歐人都好支持香港人抗擊警暴爭取基本權利。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日係721警黑勾結恐怖襲擊半週年。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e42341e3119536719e947bad97a97e14b426b71","tid":1832138,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:54:10.000Z","msg":"14號嘅新聞post 黎做乜？而且第二日已經有手足清理左<br />\n<br />\n做五毛唔該專心一啲"},{"pid":"4216d58f3912a5048401240c4e8a2a0e2964beaf","tid":1832138,"uid":306664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e42341e3119536719e947bad97a97e14b426b71","tid":1832138,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T04:54:10.000Z","msg":"14號嘅新聞post 黎做乜？而且第二日已經有手足清理左<br />\n<br />\n做五毛唔該專心一啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-21T11:50:38.000Z","msg":"我今日先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/fa